<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-10-28T10:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-10-28T10:00:00-05:00" n="1102" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1102">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">711.679 Residence and Establishment/74:
                            Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Grew</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Ankara</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-28T17:00:00+02:00">October 28, 1931—5
                                p.m.</date><lb/>[Received October 28—12:20 p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>9. Treaty of establishment and residence signed today. No alterations, no
                            procès-verbal.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi></signed></closer>
